id: pm-high
title: "mergeExtensionBlueprints: pure modular composition of partial ExtensionBlueprints"
description: "Add mergeExtensionBlueprints(...blueprints): ExtensionBlueprint to src/sdk/compose.ts — a pure, deterministic variadic merge so an author can split an extension's surface across modules/files and combine them into one blueprint for composeExtension/synthesizeExtensionManifest/preflightExtension. Merge rules: array fields (commands, preflights, itemTypes, itemFields, migrations, searchProviders, vectorStoreAdapters, importers, exporters) concatenate in order; the flags record concatenates per-command flag arrays (additive registerFlags semantics); single-handler records (commandOverrides, parsers, renderers, services) take later-blueprint-wins precedence; hooks concatenate per kind in canonical order; the imperative activate escape hatch chains in input order; deactivate chains in reverse (LIFO teardown); the manifest mirror is last-defined-wins. Returns a NEW object (never mutates inputs); zero blueprints -> {}; null/undefined fields tolerated for untyped JS authors. Duplicates surface to lintExtensionBlueprint exactly as a hand-written blueprint would."
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 2
